{"tid":1111230,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[鐵膠] 點解南昌站叫南昌站？","createTime":"2019-04-16T23:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T05:50:51.000Z","uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9adfa7ff1e6596364c6f4f538037cb142644e6e","tid":1111230,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:50:23.000Z","msg":"如果有留意到嘅話，南昌站係得去東涌嗰個月台有落地玻璃窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去東涌嗰個月台喺正個站最南面，啲窗又係向南，因為個站本身係填海區，冇地名，所以最初改站名嗰陣就睇個站設計，叫南窗站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後來覺得個同音個昌字好意頭啲，再者窗字又唔似一個地名，最後南窗站就改做南昌站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e090f8b534dc9d65fccc61e7a2cb0ec75d32cd","tid":1111230,"uid":63303,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:51:09.000Z","msg":"南昌邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c356a5a52c17ca15c191b6c6c4b7f93e54a6182","tid":1111230,"uid":245614,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:51:12.000Z","msg":"因為係南昌"},{"pid":"b3cd16c00a9ab0f3582540b3bd27c4d34956515c","tid":1111230,"uid":2757,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:52:31.000Z","msg":"點解樓主要叫月出康城呀？因為佢唔撚夠錢買日出康城囉屌...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩故仔...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0073dcc8caed261a4a72325b4cf1a4a9306a2d","tid":1111230,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"本身叫南窗站 但南窗唔好聽改左南昌"},{"pid":"4cd2376b2ac0dae0dc76541e16a008274f1ef234","tid":1111230,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9a0073dcc8caed261a4a72325b4cf1a4a9306a2d","tid":1111230,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T23:54:00.000Z","msg":"本身叫南窗站 但南窗唔好聽改左南昌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-1